<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>أَو الزَّبِيب الى البَائِع<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>كَيْلا والتخلية فِي<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
